		dependencies: ["000000000000A018"]
		title: "Wings of the Seraph"
		icon: {id: "soulland:seraph_chestplate", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Qian Renxue's path. The Seraph set emphasizes soul power output — each piece worn amplifies soul ring skill damage and meditation gains. Built for cultivation-heavy builds that want their active skills to hit harder than their weapon.", "Pairs best with the Cloth Path from Chapter 1 and a high-Intelligence stat allocation from M&S. Magic shield on top, soul skills underneath."]
		tasks: [{
