		title: "Spirit Detector"
		icon: {id: "soulland:spirit_detector", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Craft the Spirit Detector at the Forging Table. It pulses when Spirit Beasts are within range and displays approximate beast age — which tells you what ring color you're walking toward before you commit to the fight.", "A White ring is ten years. Yellow is a century. Purple is a thousand. Know before you swing."]
		tasks: [{
