		title: "Stat Point Allocation"
		icon: {id: "minecraft:book", Count: 1b}
		description: ["After applying a Stat Soul, open the Mine & Slash panel [K] to allocate the granted stat points. The options are Attack, Defense, Magic, and Speed. Your armor path from Chapter 1 tells you which column matters most for your build.", "Points from multiple souls stack. They do not expire. There is no redistribution penalty. Build what you need, adjust as your play style develops."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "000000000024A008"
			type: "checkmark"
			title: "Apply a Stat Soul and spend the points in the M&S panel [K]"
		}]
