		dependencies: ["000000000024A007", "000000000000A033"]
		title: "Rare Stat Soul"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:stat_soul/family/weapon/rare", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Rare Stat Souls require a Spirit Steel Sword as the base and a Rare Stone (stone/2) at the Gear Crafting Station. They grant 5-8 stat points each — a meaningful step up that compounds quickly when stacked.", "You need stone/2 to craft them, which comes from Act III-IV Atlas maps. The map grind and the soul grind are the same grind. Running maps generates the stones that fund better souls that let you run harder maps. The loop is intentional."]
		tasks: [{
