		title: "Epic Stat Soul"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:stat_soul/family/weapon/epic", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Epic Stat Souls use Soul Forged gear as the crafting base, an Epic Stone (stone/3), and Soul Forged Ingots at the Gear Crafting Station. Each soul grants 10-15 stat points.", "Six Epic souls on your main weapon is the EV-tier power floor. If you have completed the GT chain and the Soul Land armor track and your gear has no souls on it, you are fighting below your tier. Do this before the Ur-Ghast."]
		tasks: [{
