		x: 10.0d
		y: 4.0d
		dependencies: ["000000000024A00E"]
		title: "The Legendary Soul"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:stat_soul/family/weapon/legendary", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Legendary Stat Souls use Soul Crystal as the crafting base alongside stone/4 and Iridium at the Gear Crafting Station. Each grants 20 or more stat points.", "A full Legendary soul set takes serious endgame investment. The same Soul Crystal that feeds the Triune Catalyst also feeds the peak of the stat soul system — cultivation, combat, and arcane convergence are drawing from the same well. The result is a character that will not be challenged by anything below the hardest Atlas bosses."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "000000000024A013"
