		dependencies: ["000000000000BD01"]
		title: "Spirit Awakens"
		icon: {id: "soulland:cultivation_altar", Count: 1b}
		description: ["At Soul Power 30 the Martial Soul Transformation system unlocks its first tier. Press [V] while active — your limbs reshape. Arm fur, gauntlet overlays, and element-specific changes appear depending on your martial soul archetype.", "This is Tier 1 of three. It\'s available earlier than most players expect. You don\'t need to be near the endgame to feel the transformation system. Check your HUD after pressing V."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "000000000000EF02"
			type: "checkmark"
