		y: -4.0d
		dependencies: ["000000000000EF04"]
		title: "Spirit Avatar"
		icon: {id: "soulland:soul_crystal", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Soul Power 90. The third tier. The full Spirit Avatar — complete hybrid body transformation, every limb remade, the martial soul and the cultivator occupying the same physical form.", "The 6 Seraph wings are fully extended. For every other archetype, T3 is the form the martial soul was always building toward. It\'s the endgame shape of who you are in this system."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "000000000000EF08"
			type: "checkmark"
			title: "Reach Soul Power 90 and activate the full Spirit Avatar [V]"
		}]
		rewards: [{
