		dependencies: ["000000000000EF37"]
		title: "The Poison Path"
		icon: {id: "soulland:cultivation_manual", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Tang Sect Poison is a ten-tier system running from Numbing Powder (level 1) to Yama\'s Essence (level 90). Each poison scales its effectiveness against enemies relative to your soul power — underpowered poisons do little to strong beasts, but ranked poisons cripple them.", "Craft poisons at the Forging Table. Early tiers slow and weaken. High tiers apply stacking DOT that ignores physical resistance. Yama\'s Essence at the top has no counter in the base game."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "000000000000EF3C"
