		icon: {id: "soulland:cultivation_altar", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Ancient Spirit Incense is a consumable available at Soul Power 60+ that summons 8-12 boss-variant spirit beasts eligible for Spirit Bone drops. It\'s the primary farming tool for the Spirit Bone system.", "Craft it at the Forging Table from Soul Forged materials and rare herbs. Activate it in the Inner Forest or deeper — the summoned beasts scale to zone depth. Run it with the Beast Contract system active so you can immediately evaluate bone quality from the drops."]
		tasks: [{
