		icon: {id: "soulland:sea_god_trident", Count: 1b}
		description: ["At Soul Power 99, the Sea God path opens a Divine Inheritance Trial — a path-specific gauntlet designed for the endurance archetype. The trial tests sustained survival rather than burst damage output.", "Completing it unlocks the full Sea God Inheritance. The Sea God Trident\'s abilities scale beyond base stats when the Inheritance is active. Bring your highest-tier armor souls and a full set of Apotheosis gems in the resistance slots."]
		tasks: [{
